# CODEOWNERS — who must review and merge.
#
# Every PR against `main` requires review from a code owner listed here, and
# only a code owner can merge (enforced by branch protection). This is Kontur's
# four-eyes principle applied to its own repo: the maker never merges their own
# change.
#
# Replace the placeholder team/handles below with real GitHub teams or users
# before relying on enforcement. Order matters: the LAST matching pattern wins,
# so more specific paths override the global owner.

